data.description: This expansive home is situated on 3.5 acres, in a non-HOA neighborhood. Located 15 minutes from Lake Anna and convenient to Ashland, Richmond, and Fredericksburg!  Offering 3.052 sq. ft., 5 bedrooms, 3.5 bath, 2 car side load garage, 1 car detached rear entry garage/workshop space, a storage shed and has ground mounted SOLAR PANELS located in the rear of the property! This home features a spacious 1st floor primary bedroom with oversized jetted tub & separate shower. The large kitchen offers maple cabinets, stainless steel appliances, recessed lighting, breakfast nook and exit to the rear deck. The family room boasts vaulted ceilings, full wall of built in shelves, gas fireplace and french doors leading out to a screened porch, rear deck and stone patio, that are well suited for entertaining. The 2 story foyer leads you up to 4 bedroom and 2 full bathrooms, one on each side of the hallway! The 5th bedroom is an oversized bedroom with walk in closet and walk up attic access.  New roof installed in 2021. Drop flag pole with internal rope system and home is preregistered for Firefly Internet estimated for Spring 2024.
